pullrequest.title: Modications to ignition launch files to accomodate for spawning custom sensor configurations of x1/x2/x3/x4 from localMode.

content.raw: This PR isn’t required if submissions are forced to be prefaced by `<organization_name>`, HOWEVER we do need to think of how to catch these other model launch cases in CloudSim.
